{"tid":2499344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"守護廣東話｜英國非裔高材生自學廣東話4年 YouTube分享港式飲茶 「廣東話係好靚嘅語言，唔想佢死」","createTime":"2021-04-21T23:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T01:06:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":94,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"40ffef8c7469897e50fd9299a1343845e0544c6b","tid":2499344,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T23:24:15.000Z","msg":"現於倫敦就讀高中的Grace是愛爾蘭人，自2016年起在網上自學廣東話。通曉六種語言的她，2019年5月開設YouTube頻道，分享學習語言心得。五個月前Grace分享她在唐人街茶樓以流利廣東話點餐的影片，吸引了36.6萬人收看。現時頻道已有逾50條影片，1.3萬人訂閱。雖然學廣東話已四年，但甚有語言天份的Grace仍坦言︰「學廣東話真係好難。」<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210422/6HMEPQ5M5BDC3PD2KN55FKHZYQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210422%2F6HMEPQ5M5BDC3PD2KN55FKHZYQ%2F&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnTUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=52e6564f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210422%2F6HMEPQ5M5BDC3PD2KN55FKHZYQ%2F&h=76bff6f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210422/6HMEPQ5M5BDC3PD2KN55FKHZYQ/</a>"},{"pid":"4e7af32c066635c1b360dadfb534a2a61df6375b","tid":2499344,"uid":24160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T23:26:23.000Z","msg":"仲識法文日文。。。。好痴線"},{"pid":"e5a21824cac91c3e4229357b2279fe70545fb94f","tid":2499344,"uid":177590,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T23:27:51.000Z","msg":"連登仔矛盾大對決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f950fadd375ce6b9aa4051a7c4b6d76725b45cc0","tid":2499344,"uid":79589,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T23:30:27.000Z","msg":"廣東話係好撚靚嘅語言<br />\n屌你老母，用字加埋九音<br />\n字字鏗鏘，句句精湛"},{"pid":"2018a25697e63037c2ff9dbcfe6792c8f7875054","tid":2499344,"uid":60686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T23:38:58.000Z","msg":"好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff586a0